<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Verify Your Profile Update</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .otp-code {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c3e50;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            background-color: #f7f9fc;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .warning {
            color: #e74c3c;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Verify Your {{updateType}} Update</h2>
        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
        <p>You've requested to update your {{updateType}} on RatedaFRiKa. To verify this change, please use the following verification code:</p>
        
        <div class="otp-code">{{Otp}}</div>
        
        <p>This code will expire in {{expiryTime}}.</p>
        
        <div class="warning">
            <p>⚠️ If you didn't request this update, please:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Do not share this code with anyone</li>
                <li>Contact our support team immediately at {{supportEmail}}</li>
                <li>Consider reviewing your account security settings</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br/>RatedaFRiKa Team</p>
            <p>Need help? Contact us at {{supportEmail}}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>